commitResults.messageTitle: Rename Bot. Added Greet and Exit messages.
Added List, Add To List functionality
commitResults.messageBody:
- Refactored print method in Chatbot.java to accept String arrays
- Created Task.java to represent each user created task

- Created InputHandler.java to separate input handling from Blu.java
- Operations on list moved to TaskList.java
- Added toString method for Task to print out task's title
- Change getTask in TaskList.java to use 1-based indexing

commitResults.messageTitle: Added tracking of three subtypes of tasks
commitResults.messageBody:
- Refactored InputHandler to use switch/case statements
- Added method to retrieve number of tasks in TaskList.java
- Change addTask method in Chatbot.java to accept Task object instead

- Fixed bug in InputHandler.java where first word of deadline/event
  description was not included
- Created BluException class and three exception subclasses
  - IllegalCommand used when there are missing parameters
  - InvalidCommand used for commands that are not supported
  - IllegalParameter used when parameter does not satisfy given
    constraints
- runtest.sh now complies all java files in subdirectories

- Refactored InputHandler to call a method to validate number of command
  parameters

commitResults.messageTitle: Changed command parsing to use enums
